'''Trantor Center''' was an exercise facility located most likely in the [[Zi-Kree Sector]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It contained zero-gravity calisthenics equipment and a spa, among other things. [[Lorn Pavan]] was a frequent visitor there.

